description: Rejoice, animal lovers and herbivores alike can finally enjoy delicious barbecue at Portland's Homegrown Smoker Vegan Barbecue joint! Choose from a variety of smoked tofu, tempeh, and soy curds combinations. Menu items include the tofurrito, the smoked tempeh burger, and the carolina chickn sammich, among others. Along with your smoked non-meats, choose from a plethora of yummy veggie sides.
name: Homegrown Smoker Vegan Barbecue
